column1: Happy New Year! Wishing you a great 2020 from our family to yours. https://t.co/k3uyHehZQE
.@Mikelkehoe is doing a great job as Lieutenant Governor focusing on workforce readiness job creation and transportation. I look forward to supporting him in his campaign.
Governor @MikeParson is doing an incredible job leading our state. I look forward to his continued leadership and doing everything I can to help in his campaign.
Abby and I had a great time tonight at the annual @gcmogop bbq. Enjoyed catching up & hope to see you all again soon. https://t.co/Jqg6DBlMTc
The Jefferson County GOP put together a great event last night. Thankful for all they do to elect leaders who fight for our conservative values. https://t.co/kTAqW6AY9i

Enjoyed spending time with the Camden County GOP last night. Appreciate the opportunity to talk about all of President Trump and the GOP’s accomplishments like reshaping the judiciary putting pro-growth policies in place to get the economy humming again and much more. https://t.co/AWo3DkblfG

Great crowd at last night's @mogop_jasper - Newton County Lincoln Days dinner. Enjoyed catching up with friends and thanking them for all they do to support Republicans and fight for the conservative values we stand for. https://t.co/lr6MPmbits

With great leaders like @FitzpatrickMO and @elijahhaahr and the  dedicated men and women who were at McDonald  County Lincoln Days we are looking stronger than ever headed into 2020. Honored to be with you all today. https://t.co/F7T5vvGtAN
Always have a good time at the @GreeneComoGOP Lincoln Days. It was great to catch up and thank them for all they do to support Republicans up and down the ticket. https://t.co/mYBgZAkFBb
